column5: That went and dumped all this white crap all over my back yard...I guess I wont be mowing the lawn for a while now  :dunno:
Same problem here ! Ans snowing now, it melts when it hits the ground but the roofs are white. Shouldn't have started the snowblower last Sunday
We got 10 cm here yesterday.  Won't be long now
I'll be looking for some footie prints tomorrow.

none here its illegal till Christmas day. I passed a bylaw
